Title: An Act Changing the Name of Numancia Elementary School Located in the Municipality of Numancia, Province of Aklan, to Rajah Bangkaya Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 778
An Act Changing the Name of Numancia Elementary School Located in the Municipality of Numancia, Province of Aklan, to Rajah Bangkaya Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Numancia Elementary School located in the Municipality of Numancia, Province of Aklan, is hereby changed to Rajah Bangkaya Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
